on Johnston (wrestler)|Cameron Johnston]]|AUS|2000 Summer}}\n|3||1||2||4||0\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Ruslan Veliyev]]|KAZ|2000 Summer}}\n|3||0||3||1||1\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size:90% \"\n! align=\"right\" width=\"250\"|\n!width=\"60\"|Score\n!align=\"left\" width=\"250\"|\n! width=\"60\" | {{Tooltip|CP|Classification points}}\n|- \n|align=\"left\"| '''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Almazbek Askarov]]|KGZ|2000 Summer}}'''|| '''3\u20131'''||align=\"left\"| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Ruslan Veliyev]]|KAZ|2000 Summer}}||3\u20131 '''PP'''\n|- \n|align=\"left\"| '''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Sergey Demchenko]]|BLR|2000 Summer}}'''|| '''10\u20130'''||align=\"left\"| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Cameron Johnston (wrestler)|Cameron Johnston]]|AUS|2000 Summer}}||4\u20130 '''ST'''\n|- \n|align=\"left\"| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Almazbek Askarov]]|KGZ|2000 Summer}} || '''0\u20133'''||align=\"left\"| '''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Sergey Demchenko]]|BLR|2000 Summer}}'''||0\u20133 '''PO'''\n|- \n|align=\"left\"| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Ruslan Veliyev]]|KAZ|2000 Summer}} || ||align=\"left\"| '''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Cameron Johnston (wrestler)|Cameron Johnston]]|AUS|2000 Summer}}'''||0\u20134 '''PA'''\n|- \n|align=\"left\"| '''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Almazbek Askarov]]|KGZ|2000 Summer}}'''|| '''10\u20130'''||align=\"left\"| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Cameron Johnston (wrestler)|Cameron Johnston]]|AUS|2000 Summer}}||4\u20130 '''ST'''\n|- \n|align=\"left\"| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Ruslan Veliyev]]|KAZ|2000 Summer}} || ||align=\"left\"| '''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Sergey Demchenko]]|BLR|2000 Summer}}'''||0\u20134 '''PA'''\n|}\n\n===Knockout round ===\n{{8TeamBracket-Compact-NoSeeds-Byes\n|RD1=Quarterfinals\n|RD2=Semifinals\n|RD3=Gold medal match\n|RD3b=Bronze medal match\n\n| team-width=195\n| score-width=30\n\n| RD1-team01='''{{flagIOCathlete|[[Daniel Igali]]|CAN|2000 Summer}}'''\n| RD1-score01='''3'''\n| RD1-team02={{flagIOCathlete|[[Yosvany S\u00e1nchez]]|CUB|2000 Summer}}\n| RD1-score02=1\n\n| R