jid Aflaki]]\n|[[Taekwondo at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 80 kg|80 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[V\u00edctor Estrada|Estrada]]|MEX|2000 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 3\u2013'''4'''\n|colspan=4 align=center|Did not advance\n|align=center|'''11'''\n|}\n\n===Weightlifting ===\n{{main|Weightlifting at the 2000 Summer Olympics}}\n\n;Men<ref>{{cite web|url=http://la84foundation.org/6oic/OfficialReports/2000/Masters/wl/WLresults.pdf|title=Official Report of the XXVII Olympiad \u2013 Results \u2013 Weightlifting|date=4 January 2011|publisher=[[LA84 Foundation]]|pages=35\u201341|accessdate=19 June 2011}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=\"60%\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%\"\n|-\n!width=\"20%\"|Athlete\n!width=\"8%\"|Event\n!width=\"11%\"|Snatch\n!width=\"11%\"|Clean & Jerk\n!width=\"13%\"|Total\n!width=\"6%\"|Rank\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Mehdi Panzvan]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Weightlifting at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 62 kg|62 kg]]\n|140.0\n|162.5\n|302.5\n|'''5'''\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Mohammad Hossein Barkhah]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Weightlifting at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 77 kg|77 kg]]\n|No mark\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|'''\u2014'''\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Shahin Nassirinia]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Weightlifting at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 85 kg|85 kg]]\n|No mark\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|'''\u2014'''\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Kourosh Bagheri]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[Weightlifting at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 94 kg|94 kg]]\n|187.5\n|215.0\n|402.5\n|'''4'''\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''[[Hossein Tavakkoli]]'''\n|align=\"left\"|[[Weightlifting at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 105 kg|105 kg]]\n|190.0\n|235.0\n|425.0\n|{{Gold1}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''[[Hossein Rezazadeh]]'''\n|align=\"left\"|[[Weightlifting at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's +105 kg|+105 kg]]\n|212.5 '''[[List of world records in Olympic weightlifting|WR]]'''\n|260.0\n|472.5 '''[[List of world records in Olympic weightlifting|WR]]'''\n|{{Gold1}}\n|}\n\n===Wrestlin